# FileFree Strategy Context

## Co-Founder Operating Model

FileFree is built and operated by two co-founders with AI agents as the extended team:

- **Product/Engineering** (Founder 1): AI coding agents (Cursor) handle implementation. Reviews, tests, deploys. Owns product, infrastructure, tax calculations, OCR pipeline, content creation, EFIN/IRS certification.
- **Partnerships/Revenue** (Founder 2): FAANG partnerships background. Owns partner outreach, deal negotiation, revenue stream activation. AI persona (partnerships.mdc) handles research, drafts, and pipeline tracking. Target: 2-3 hours/week.
- **Growth**: AI drafts content, SEO articles, social media copy. Founder 1 records videos, publishes.
- **Strategy**: AI analyzes data, drafts plans, logs decisions. Both co-founders make final calls.
- **Legal**: AI drafts policies, checklists, disclaimers. Founder 1 executes filings. Founder 2 reviews partnership agreements.

## Notion Workspace Structure (Company HQ)

**Pages:**
- Strategy & Vision — north star, competitive landscape, moats
- Product Roadmap — sprint board, task status, blockers
- Decision Log — every strategic decision with date, rationale, alternatives
- Content Calendar — social posts, articles, video scripts (planned/published)
- Legal & Compliance — EFIN status, privacy policy drafts, ToS, disclaimers
- Financials — costs, revenue tracking, unit economics
- Partnerships — Column Tax, financial product referrals, creator outreach

## Decision Log Format

Every significant decision gets logged:

```
Date: YYYY-MM-DD
Decision: [What was decided]
Context: [Why this came up]
Alternatives: [What else was considered]
Rationale: [Why this option won]
Reversibility: [Easy/Medium/Hard to undo]
```

## Weekly Operating Cadence

**Monday**: Review metrics (PostHog), check Sentry errors, plan the week's code tasks
**Tuesday-Thursday**: Build (AI-agent-assisted coding sessions)
**Friday**: Content day — record videos, publish articles, social posts
**Weekend**: Strategy review — update Notion, log decisions, plan next week

